Biography

Dawn Taylor, MSN, APRN, FNP-C, is an advanced practice registered nurse. Dawn received her Associate of Science in Nursing degree from Valencia College and her Bachelor of Science in Nursing degree from Jacksonville University. She completed a Master of Science in Nursing degree with a focus as a Family Nurse Practitioner from AdventHealth University. Dawn is a member of the American Academy of Nurse Practitioners.

A highly experienced clinician, Dawn Taylor has been with AdventHealth for nearly 17 years serving in various nursing, nursing leadership, and nursing administration roles at AdventHealth Altamonte and AdventHealth Orlando. Dawn aligns with our Mission and Vision to provide whole-person care as an extension of Christ. Dawn truly values the experience of her patients and their families and is honored to be a partner in their health.
